(13, 'Use Captivating Headlines', 'use-captivating-headlines', '1687259219.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:21px;padding-left:100px;font-family:charter;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(37,37,37);\">Your blog post headline should be compelling and at the same time meaningful. Considering that <a href=\"https://moz.com/blog/5-data-insights-into-the-headlines-readers-click\" style=\"color:rgb(37,37,37);\">80% of readers never make it past the headline</a>, you have to prioritize it and make sure it hooks your readers from the very start. Here are some tactics that have proven to be effective:</p><ul><li style=\"margin-left:15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Number headlines</span>. These headlines are effective as the human eye is attracted to numbers placed side-by-side with plain text.<span style=\"font-weight:700;\"> </span></li><li style=\"margin-left:15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Ask questions</span>. These headlines grab your readers’ attention by getting them to think, or to seek to understand the subject matter.</li><li style=\"margin-left:15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Create a sense of awe in the minds of your readers</span>. These headlines usually draw the attention of their readers by presenting the subject matter in an unusual way</li><li style=\"margin-left:15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Educational headlines</span>. These are headlines that typically use “How to…”</li></ul>', 1, 72, 9, 42, 'Our Blogs', 'Web development is an ever-evolving field that requires a wide range of skills to build Blog', '2023-06-20 20:36:59', '2023-06-20 20:36:59'),
(14, 'Provide Meaningful Value', 'provide-meaningful-value', '1687259356.jpg', '<p style=\"font-size:21px;padding-left:100px;font-family:charter;line-height:1.6;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;color:rgb(37,37,37);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Ultimately, your blog title should tell your readers what they’ll learn from reading your blog and what value will you provide to them with your article. How you present the value your article promises to deliver is what gets your readers to either click-through or to move on to another piece of content.</p>', 2, 72, 9, 42, 'Article', 'Keep your blog titles clear, concise, and free of irrelevant/vague words that don’t describe the crux of your article and are incapable of getting your target audience to read and/or share your article.', '2023-06-20 20:39:16', '2023-06-20 20:39:16'),
(15, '4. Optimize for SEO', '4.-optimize-for-seo', '1687259435.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:21px;padding-left:100px;font-family:charter;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(37,37,37);\">When brainstorming for blog titles, there’s an important question you need to ask yourself, and that question is: What’s the motivation behind my readers researching this subject on search engines?</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:21px;padding-left:100px;font-family:charter;line-height:1.6;color:rgb(37,37,37);\">With this in mind, you can begin to draft your title and include the keywords your users typically use in their search query.</p><div><br /></div>', 3, 72, 9, 42, 'Seo', 'Analyze your best performing blog posts and their titles, and try to find out which ones generated the most clicks and why. Are there specific trends you can identify, for example, when comparing 2-3 articles on similar topics?\r\n\r\nThis data is beneficial as it lets you know what to focus on when creating a title for your next blog article.', '2023-06-20 20:40:35', '2023-06-20 20:40:35'),
(16, 'Management, Security & Governance', 'management,-security-&-governance', '1687331047.png', '<div><div style=\"margin-left:auto;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div><div><div><div style=\"font-family:JioType, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1.125rem;line-height:1.33333;text-align:left;\"><p>Implementing JioCloud Management, security and governance services, businesses can channelise on building the core of the business rather than focussing on technology enablers such as apps, infrastructure, and network. JioCloud offers versatile portfolios which manages all the important layers of infrastructure and its stack end-to-end. Jio’s process framework includes assessing business requirements considering it’s prospective impact on IT architecture framework and analyzing new IT requirements that could be addressed with the solution.</p><div style=\"font-size:1.5rem;line-height:1.33333;\">Simplify, automate, and optimize the management &amp; compliance of Cloud resources with secure end-end management of infrastructure</div><div><br /></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 1, 76, 10, 44, 'Manage & govern all Cloud infrastructure at a single place', 'Simplify, automate, and optimize the management & compliance of Cloud resources with secure end-end management of infrastructure', '2023-06-21 16:34:07', '2023-06-21 16:34:07'),
(17, 'Datacenter Transformation', 'datacenter-transformation', '1687331160.jpg', '<div><div style=\"margin-left:auto;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div><div><div><div style=\"font-family:JioType, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1.125rem;line-height:1.33333;text-align:left;\"><p>In today\'s digital world, providing a great customer experience anytime, anywhere is the top most priority for any business. This warrants for real-time access to information and a fundamental shift in the way we manage our data.</p><p>To keep up with these changing needs, businesses are rapidly opting for public and private Clouds, edge Clouds and co-location facilities. They are also looking at evolving their datacenters using virtualization and software-defined networks.</p><p>If not done in a structured manner datacenter transformation, consolidation, and migration projects can stretch the organization\'s IT teams operations and challenge the team\'s skillset and procedures. Datacenter transformation solution can helps solve these problems by synergizing with JioCloud Services and help in meeting your business goal.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 2, 76, 10, 44, 'Migrate data centers and automate business processes', 'Transform your business by adopting scalable, agile, and automated IT processes, with JioCloud datacenter transformation solutions', '2023-06-21 16:36:00', '2023-06-21 16:36:00'),
(18, 'Application Modernization', 'application-modernization', '1687331484.jpg', '<div><div style=\"margin-left:auto;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div><div><div><div style=\"font-family:JioType, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1.125rem;line-height:1.33333;text-align:left;\"><p>The world is moving away from siloed, monolithic, under or oversized infrastructure and complex architecture to a unified and standard way of application management and deployment. The way forward for application modernization across most firms today is to make provision for necessary infrastructure in a matter of seconds by leveraging virtual machines, software, and databases over the Cloud.</p><p>Jio\'s framework for Cloud transformation is built on a two-pronged approach i.e. Assessment of business requirements considering impact on existing IT architecture, analysing and recommending the necessary transformative strategies for application modernization.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 3, 76, 10, 44, 'Modernize applications by leveraging the power of Cloud', 'Unleash the full potential of your applications by seamlessly migrating to containers, managed databases and serverless services', '2023-06-21 16:41:24', '2023-06-21 16:41:24'),
(19, 'Data Analytics', 'data-analytics', '1687331571.jpg', '<div><div style=\"margin-left:auto;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div><div><div><div style=\"font-family:JioType, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1.125rem;line-height:1.33333;text-align:left;\"><p>Billions of Gigabyte data is being generated in day-today business operations, there is a critical need for businesses to be able to analyse and use it for gaining insights for data driven decision making.</p><p>Jio\'s Data Analytics services helps to achieve the desired capabilities by empowering data scientists and developers with a wide range of productive experiences to build, train, and deploy machine learning models and foster team collaboration. These services include Analytics, AI + ML, Security, Identity, etc. to boost productivity of your business. Start transforming your business in the data ecosystem, by adopting these new technologies in data analytics over the Cloud with on-demand and pay-as-you-go model.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 4, 76, 10, 44, 'Enable strategic decision making with advanced analytics', 'Improve data-driven decisions using artificial intelligence, machine learning by leveraging JioCloud solutions', '2023-06-21 16:42:51', '2023-06-21 16:42:51'),
(20, 'Top Tips for Freelancers: Balancing Work and Personal Life', 'top-tips-for-freelancers:-balancing-work-and-personal-life', '1688563494.jpg', '<p style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">Subtitle: \"Achieving Work-Life Balance as a Freelancer\"</span><br /></p><p style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\">Introduction: In the world of freelancing, finding a healthy work-life balance can be challenging. Juggling multiple clients, deadlines, and personal commitments requires careful planning and self-discipline. In this blog post, we will share valuable tips to help freelancers achieve a harmonious balance between work and personal life, ensuring productivity, well-being, and satisfaction.</p><ol><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Set Clear Boundaries: Establishing clear boundaries between work and personal life is crucial. Define specific work hours and stick to them, avoiding the temptation to work beyond your designated time. Communicate these boundaries to your clients and let them know when you are available and when you are not.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Prioritize Self-Care: Freelancers often neglect self-care while trying to meet client demands. Make time for exercise, relaxation, and hobbies to recharge your mind and body. Taking breaks throughout the day will improve focus and productivity when you are working.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Create a Dedicated Workspace: Designate a specific area in your home as your workspace. This will help create a physical separation between work and personal life, enabling better focus and concentration during work hours. At the end of the day, step away from your workspace to relax and unwind.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Plan and Organize: Develop a schedule or use productivity tools to plan your work and personal tasks. Set realistic deadlines and allocate time for each task, ensuring a balanced workload. Regularly review and update your schedule to accommodate changing priorities.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Learn to Say No: It\'s essential to learn to say no to projects or tasks that don\'t align with your goals or overwhelm your workload. By prioritizing and selectively choosing projects, you can maintain a manageable workload and avoid burnout.</p></li></ol><p style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\">Conclusion: Achieving work-life balance as a freelancer requires conscious effort and a commitment to self-care. By setting boundaries, prioritizing self-care, creating a dedicated workspace, planning effectively, and learning to say no, freelancers can enjoy a fulfilling and balanced lifestyle.</p>', 1, 73, 11, 43, '#blog,#work', NULL, '2023-06-21 19:02:54', '2023-07-05 22:54:54'),
(21, 'Networking Tips for Freelancers: Building Connections and Growing Your Business', 'networking-tips-for-freelancers:-building-connections-and-growing-your-business', '1688563392.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\">Subtitle: \"Harnessing the Power of Networking in the Freelance World\"</span></p><p style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\">Introduction: Networking is a valuable tool for freelancers to expand their professional network, gain new clients, and unlock business opportunities. In this blog post, we will share essential networking tips specifically tailored for freelancers. By implementing these strategies, you can enhance your visibility, establish meaningful connections, and grow your freelance business.</p><ol><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Attend Industry Events and Meetups: Participate in relevant industry events, conferences, and meetups to meet potential clients and like-minded professionals. Engage in conversations, exchange business cards, and build connections. Networking in person provides a personal touch that can be highly beneficial in building trust and rapport.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Utilize Online Platforms: Leverage online platforms, such as LinkedIn, freelance marketplaces, and professional forums, to connect with fellow freelancers, industry experts, and potential clients. Build a compelling profile that highlights your expertise, skills, and past successes. Engage in discussions, share valuable insights, and participate in relevant groups to expand your online presence.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Offer Value and Collaboration: Networking is a two-way street. Offer your expertise and support to others by providing helpful insights, advice, or collaboration opportunities. By demonstrating your willingness to contribute, you build credibility and foster mutually beneficial relationships.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Follow Up and Nurture Connections: After meeting someone, follow up with a personalized message or email to express your appreciation for the connection. Stay in touch periodically by sharing relevant industry news or updates. Nurturing relationships over time can lead to referrals and future collaboration opportunities.</p></li><li style=\"padding-left:0.375em;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Attend Webinars and Online Workshops: Participate in webinars, online workshops, and virtual conferences that are relevant to your industry. Engage with the speakers and other attendees through chat features or Q&amp;A sessions. Virtual networking can be just as impactful in expanding your professional network.</p></li></ol><p style=\"color:rgb(55,65,81);font-family:\'Söhne\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(247,247,248);\">Conclusion: Networking plays a vital role in the success of freelancers. By attending industry events, utilizing online platforms, offering value, following up, and participating in webinars, freelancers can establish strong connections, foster collaborations, and unlock new business opportunities. Building a robust professional network is an ongoing process that can significantly contribute to the growth and success of your freelance business.</p><p><br /></p>', 2, 73, 12, 43, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-21 19:18:47', '2023-07-05 22:53:12'),
(24, 'New Figma Features', 'new-figma-features', '1687852197.jpg', '<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:\'hex-franklin-variable\';font-size:18px;\">While the Figma canvas is great for freeform design exploration, it can be confusing if you’re dropped into a design file that’s missing information needed for implementation. Dev Mode is like a browser inspector for your design file, and it brings design concepts—shapes, layers, and groups—closer to developer concepts like code, icons, and tokens. By hovering and clicking around the Figma canvas, you can find and export all the information you need, like measurements, specs, and assets, and uncover additional context from your design system. Much like </span><a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/docs/devtools/\" style=\"font-family:\'hex-franklin-variable\';font-size:18px;\">Chrome Dev Tools</a><span style=\"font-family:\'hex-franklin-variable\';font-size:18px;\">, Dev Mode takes inspiration from other development tools to create an environment that’s immediately familiar to you.</span></span>', 1, 81, 13, 46, 'Figma,dev mode,design,development,figma new feature', 'Design and development, finally on the same page', '2023-06-27 17:02:20', '2023-06-27 17:19:57'),
(25, 'Stunning and empowering artwork', 'stunning-and-empowering-artwork', '1687851719.jpg', '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:ABCDiatype, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">Multi-disciplined creative and globetrotter </span><a href=\"https://marianavarrosanchez.myportfolio.com/home\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:ABCDiatype, sans-serif;font-size:26px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Maria Navarro Sanchez</span></a><span style=\"font-family:ABCDiatype, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"> combines illustration and design to create stunning and empowering artwork.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:ABCDiatype, sans-serif;\">Based in the German city of Karlsruhe, illustrator and designer Maria Navarro Sanchez\'s career has been meandering. These days she works as a self-taught illustrator, creating art for the likes of The New Yorker and Adidas, but she originally started out by studying audiovisual communication in Malaga. After this, she completed an MA in graphic design.</span><br /></p><p style=\"margin-left:auto;font-family:ABCDiatype, sans-serif;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">\"I always knew I wanted to do something creative, but I didn\'t know exactly what,\" Maria tells Creative Boom. To combat this common creative stumbling block, Maria went to China and studied the language at Xian and Shanghai universities for three semesters. And with Spain\'s economic situation so difficult then, she decided to remain in China.</span></p><p><br /></p>', 3, 81, 14, 46, 'graphic,design,illustraions', 'stunning and empowering artwork\r\nillustration and design', '2023-06-27 17:11:59', '2023-06-27 17:11:59'),
(26, 'Let\'s Know About How To Design  Brand Guidelines', 'let\'s-know-about-how-to-design-brand-guidelines', '1687856290.jpg', '<p>Let\'s Know About Brand Guidelines<br /></p>', 5, 81, 14, 46, 'brand,brand guidelines', NULL, '2023-06-27 18:28:10', '2023-06-27 18:29:19'),
