(10, '1687239626.png', 'Ui Dev', 'UI UX design', 'Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old.', 3, 53, 1, '2023-06-20 15:10:26', '2023-06-20 15:10:26'),
(11, '1687241341.jpg', 'Sarah Connor', 'web developer', '\"Working with Sarah was a pleasure. Her creativity and ability to capture our vision were impressive. She always exceeded our expectations, and I highly recommend her for any design project.\"', 3, 70, 40, '2023-06-20 15:39:01', '2023-06-20 15:39:01'),
(13, '1687249297.jpg', 'Devin kaur', 'CEO', 'I am writing this testimonial to express my utmost satisfaction with the services provided by XYZ IT Business. As a small business owner, I understand the importance of having reliable and efficient IT solutions, and XYZ IT Business has consistently delivered exceptional results.', 1, 72, 42, '2023-06-20 17:51:37', '2023-06-20 17:52:32'),
(14, '1687249406.jpg', 'Devin kaur', 'CEO', 'From the initial consultation to the implementation and ongoing support, the team at XYZ IT Business has demonstrated a high level of professionalism and expertise. They took the time to understand our unique business needs and offered tailored solutions that have greatly enhanced our operations.', 2, 72, 42, '2023-06-20 17:53:26', '2023-06-20 17:53:26'),
(15, '1687249450.jpg', 'Devin kaur', 'CEO', 'One aspect that stands out is their prompt response time. Whenever we have encountered any technical issues or needed assistance, the XYZ IT Business team has been readily available to provide timely support. Their knowledgeable technicians have resolved our problems quickly, minimizing any downtime and ensuring that our business continues to run smoothly.', 3, 72, 42, '2023-06-20 17:54:10', '2023-06-20 17:54:10'),
(16, '1687249484.jpg', 'Devin kaur', 'CEO', 'Moreover, XYZ IT Business has proactively kept us updated on the latest advancements in IT technology and recommended innovative solutions to improve our efficiency and security. They have implemented robust cybersecurity measures to protect our data and provided valuable advice on backup and disaster recovery strategies.', 4, 72, 42, '2023-06-20 17:54:44', '2023-06-20 17:54:44'),
(17, '1687331783.jpg', 'Specificity', 'CEO', 'The testimonial gives a specific reason why a service or product was good. This specificity boosts credibility, and it makes the testimonial feel more authentic—readers know the writer of the testimonial actually experienced a good service.', 1, 76, 44, '2023-06-21 16:46:23', '2023-06-21 16:46:23'),
(18, '1687331847.jpg', 'Explanation of a benefit', 'CEO', 'A good testimonial demonstrates what impact a product or service had on the client; it shows how their lives have improved. This is what makes others interested in buying, too.', 2, 76, 44, '2023-06-21 16:47:27', '2023-06-21 16:47:27'),
(19, '1687331909.jpg', 'Web Development', 'CEO', 'Front-end web development has to do with the interface that you, the user, interact with when you visit a website or use a web application. Front-End Developers create everything you see on a web page, including', 3, 76, 44, '2023-06-21 16:48:29', '2023-06-26 19:43:47'),
(20, '1687331967.jpg', 'Web Development', 'CEO', 'I sailed through the course in about 10 days because it’s sectioned into digestible modules that kept me curious to learn more. My copywriting skills have improved drastically and I’ve taken up a new interest in the world of copywriting. Thank you, Henneke!', 4, 76, 44, '2023-06-21 16:49:27', '2023-06-21 16:49:27'),
(22, '1688478684.jpg', 'Project: \"Website Redesign for ABC Company\"', 'Testimonial from ABC Company', '\"Working with John Doe on our website redesign project was an absolute pleasure. Their expertise in web design and development helped us transform our outdated website into a modern and visually appealing online presence. They understood our brand identity and translated it beautifully into the design elements, ensuring a seamless user experience across different devices.\"', 2, 73, 43, '2023-06-21 20:04:48', '2023-07-04 23:21:24'),
(23, '1687929156.jpg', 'Daren Hatcher', 'Founder', 'It was a pleasure working with Margie. She did a awesome and creative graphics for digital campaign. She always exceeded our expectations, and I highly recommend her for any design project.', 1, 81, 46, '2023-06-28 14:42:36', '2023-06-28 14:42:36'),
